content:
POST /problems/:id/submit -> Submission
{
  code: string,
  language: string
}

- userId not passed into the API, we can assume the user is authenticated and the userId is stored in the session

{
  id: string,
  title: string,
  question: string,
  level: string,
  tags: string[],
  codeStubs: {
    python: string,
    javascript: string,
    typescript: string,
    ...
  },
  testCases: {
    type: string,
    input: string,
    output: string
  }[]
}

{
  "id": 1,
  "title": "Max Depth of Binary Tree",
  ...
  "testCases": [
    {
      "type": "tree",
      "input": [3,9,20,null,null,15,7],
      "output": 3
    },
    {
      "type": "tree",
      "input": [1,null,2],
      "output": 2
    }
  ]
}
